{
  "stem": "26728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These-- these PE instructors just were the boss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would make-- you never walked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You ran every place you went for 8 to 12 hours a day, every day, seven days a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were training you to be tough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you are going to be a paratrooper, and that was the bottom line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I went through that class, got my mandatory five jumps in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was asked if I would like to be an instructor because I was in very good physical condition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could run all day, 20, 30 miles a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I weighed about a 160 pounds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my F-- my youth with-- as a football player-- all that really had now began to pay off for me because I was really in good-- in good condition.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I became a PE instructor with a promise of a promotion from the commanding officer of the-- of the Fort Benning, Georgia jump school, who was Colonel Bronko Nagurski who was a professional wrestler in the old days.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You may have heard of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a football player, All-American football player, and he was also a professional wrestler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Huge-- Could you repeat his name?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bronko Nagurski.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met the man twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was awesome.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nice, but he was awesome.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a colonel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, anyhow, he was the one that gave me the opportunity to become an constructor, which meant, OK, if they do go overseas-- this was my thinking-- I won't have to go as long as I'm here.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I had to make a jump a month, you know, to-- to keep my-- to get my jump pay, which is 50% of your base pay.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I made 5 jumps, and I didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
